<specimenCount id="9D2DB1D7CB3EC20FCD08FF03FB81C026" box="[873,1033,232,258]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
in which it is entirely ferruginous.
</paragraph>
